00251 BrisaControlPointService *BrisaControlPointDevice::getServiceById(QString serviceId) {
00252     for (int i = 0; i < this->serviceList.size(); i++) {
00253         if (this->serviceList.at(i)->getAttribute(BrisaControlPointService::ServiceId).compare(serviceId) == 0) {
